title: Celine Teen Triomphe Bag
description: Celine Teen Triomphe bag in Triomphe canvas and brown smooth calfskin leather. Featuring gold-toned hardware, adjustable leather shoulder strap and a front flap with signature Celine logo. The push-lock closure opens to a partitioned brown leather interior with a front pocket and a zip pocket. Approx. dimensions: 19cm(W) x 14cm(H) x 6cm(D), and 49cm adjustable shoulder drop. Accompanied by a Celine dustbag and care card. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
